name: Romanian Black Sea Phytoplankton data from 1981 to 1990
description: The phytoplankton dataset includes samples collected fromshallow to shelf Romanianwaters, in the period 1981 - 1990,from February to November;there is no similar frequency each year. Dataset contains abundance data (cells per liter) and biomass (mg/m3) for individual phytoplanktontaxa.
